Ralf on joining Man Utd:<br />
<br />
&lsquo;So would Rangnick, a sporting director with a proven track record, be interested in an approach from Old Trafford? &ldquo;I am happy where I am but if any club wanted to speak to me, the question would have to be: &lsquo;Can I be somebody who can influence areas of development across the whole club?&rsquo; Otherwise you are only getting half of what I am capable of. If, after that, you can work together in a trustworthy and respectful way, then you are more likely to be successful.&rdquo;

